## How to set up a design history site

Full guidance on how to set up, make changes and host your design history can be found on the documentation site:

<a href="https://design-history.herokuapp.com/set-up-a-design-history/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">https://design-history.herokuapp.com/set-up-a-design-history/</a>

### Quick start

Visit the the <a href="https://github.com/x-govuk/govuk-design-history" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">govuk-design-history repository</a> on GitHub, and click 'Use this template' and follow the instructions to get started.


